data.title: Fine Gael – Putting Money Back in People’s Pockets
data.meta_description: Fine Gael is putting money back in people's pockets to help with the cost of living.
data.text:
Free schoolbooks ease back to school burden – Dolan

Free schoolbooks will ease the financial pressures on parents of primary and secondary school students, a Fine Gael Senator has said.

12th August 2024

Further investment needed into women’s football – Carrigy

More facilities need to be provided for the increase in women playing soccer across Ireland, a Fine Gael Senator has said.

10th August 2024

Contactless payments for public transport must be fast tracked – Tormey

The current timeline to introduce contactless payments for public transport is far too long, a Fine Gael Councillor has said.

7th August 2024
